                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/3580" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0308</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10908 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新地地产传统HR转型BP：跳出专业领地与业务共舞</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Xindi&#39;s Human Resource Management Transition From Traditional HR to BP : Jump Out Of Professional Territory and Dance With The Business</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">奚菁，罗智玲</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广东工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新地房地产经纪有限公司佛山分公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">房地产行业；HRBP；人力资源三支柱；组织变革；2018百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Real estate industry; HRBP; HRCOE; Three pillars of human resources management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例以2016年国家宏观调控导致房地产市场萎靡为背景，描述了新地房地产经纪有限公司佛山分公司为摆脱所面临的业务人员流失率居高不下、业绩持续下滑的困境，对传统的模块化人力资源管理进行HRBP转型的全过程。此次转型以更近距离地洞察组织经营环境的变化、更有力地支持组织战略的实现为目的，过程包括HRBP转型方案的设计、转型过程的策划、转型项目落地保障措施等。案例对该过程中企业遇到的问题及其应对方案进行了详细描述。本案例适用于人力资源管理课程的教学，尤其是关于战略人力资源管理的主题，也为了解实践中企业如何进行HRBP转型提供了全面而真实的分析场景。本案例也适用于组织行为学课程中以组织变革为主题的教学，学生可学习如何运用组织变革动力、变革过程和变革策略等理论解决实际问题。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In this case, with the background of the national macro-control in 2016 causing the real estate market to be sluggish. Describes the whole process of the HRBP transformation of the traditional modular human resource management in order to get rid of the dilemma that the loss rate of the business staff is high and the performance continues to decline. This process aims at providing closer insights into changes in the organization&#39;s business environment and supporting organization strategies more effectively. The content includes the design of transformation programs, the planning of the transformation process, and the safeguard measures taken to implement the transformation projects. The case details the problems encountered in the process and their solutions. This case is applicable to the teaching of human resource management courses, especially the topic of strategic human resource management, and also provides a comprehensive and realistic analysis scenario for understanding how enterprises conduct HRBP transformation in practice. This case also applies to the teaching of organizational behavior, especially the topic of organizational change. Students can use this case to learn the dynamics of organizational change, the process of change, and the embodiment of change strategies in practice.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略人力资源管理、组织变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2018-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
